Input/Output path and filename:
Visual               vis_path (Path name for visualization files)
Restart              restart_path (Path name for restart files)
Stats                stats_path (Path name for statistics files)
Probe                probe_path (Path name for probe measurements)
Source               source_path (Path name for noise source data)
srm                  prefix (Prefix for output files)

Grid parameters:
1                    Grid_X (Spec for x-grid, 1:uniform; 2:stretch)
1                    Grid_Y (Spec for y-grid, 1:uniform; 2:erf)
0d0                  x_start (Start point in x-direction)
0d0                  y_start (Start point in y-direction)
0d0                  z_start (Start point in z-direction)
1.5d0                period_x (Domain length in x-direction)
1.5d0                period_y (Domain length in y-direction)
1.5d0                period_z (Domain length in z-direction)

Flow parameters:
0d0                  Re (Reynolds number: inertial to viscous forces)
0d0                  Pr (Prandtl number)
1d0                  Sc (Schmidt number)
1.4d0                gamma1 (Specific heat ratio of gas 1)
1.09d0               gamma2 (Specific heat ratio of gas 2)
0.198265856d0        epsilon (Ratio of molecular weights = M1/M2)
0.76d0               vis_exp (Exponent of viscosity power law)
0.0d0                bulk_ratio (Bulk to shear viscosity ratio)
1d0                  T_ratio (Temperature ratio)
1                    hyper_param (0: hyperviscosity off, 1: on)

Time advancement parameters:
1                    march_mode (1,2:Nsteps; 3,4:time; 1,3:CFL; 2,4:dt)
0.125d-1             Tstep (Time step)
0.1d0                cfl_cal (CFL in computation)
20                   Nsteps (# of time steps to take)
4200d0               run_time (Computation time in wall seconds)
1                    comp_stats (# of time step to accumulate stats)

Input/Output parameters:
1                    out_grid (Write the grid, 1:write)
1                    out_init (Write the initial field, 1:write)
1                    out_incr_x (Output increment in x-grid)
1                    out_incr_y (Output increment in y-grid)
1                    out_incr_z (Output increment in z-grid)
1000                out_restart (# of time step to write restart file)
500                 out_vis (# of time step to write visual results)
1000                out_probe (# of time step to write probe data)
1000                out_stats (# of time step to write turb stats)
1000                out_source (# of time step to write noise source)
